Module 3 - Topic 1: Adding Features, One by One
https://www.youtube.com/watch?feature=player_embedded&v=EwA3rJvKB0w
Which of the following are the steps we should use to iteratively add features to our game?
Your answer: Select, code and test each feature.
The iterative development processes are designed to maintain control over the addition of new features to achieve high quality outcomes. By clearly identifying what should be added, coding and testing each feature, there is a controlled process.

